data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and cozy property! It consists of 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, ceramic floors except the rooms that contain carpets. The kitchen offers Stainless Steel appliances, beautiful quartz countertops and a beautiful island. Both bathrooms offer quartz countertops. This property offers Solar System, convenient for electricity savings (paid), Fully fenced yard convenient for family activities, privacy or pets, exterior rear floor in pavers ready to build a beautiful terrace. The property offers direct access to the backyard through a private gate, 12x11 Concrete Floor in the backyard that can be used to park additional vehicles, etc. Closed garage with garage door for 2 vehicles that includes operator and wireless controls, Ring doorbell with camera located at the entrance of the property, ideal for privacy and security. Just walking distance to Commerce, Dining and Entertainment, just minutes from Posner Park Outlet Mall, including Disney World at 27 minutes, 19 miles. This property is ready to welcome you and your family as owners, or for investors looking for a good return on their investment.
